HEADWORD: Chemist
<hw>Chem"ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Shortened from
<ets>alchemist</ets>; cf. F. <ets>chimiste</ets>.]</ety> <def>A person
versed in chemistry or given to chemical investigation; an analyst; a
maker or seller of chemicals or drugs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

